data.title: PHOTOS: Area schools well-represented at state track meet
data.meta_description: The high school sports season wraps up with the KSHSAA all-classes state track and field meet Friday and Saturday, May 24-25, 2024, on the campus of Wichita State University.
data.text:
Lewis Marien

Staff Photographer
